section: 5. Delivery

deadline: Delivery to Salwa Industrial Area warehouse | date: 2026-07-22 | consequence: 0.5% of PO value per week late, capped at 5%

delivery-term: DAP Salwa Industrial Area, Doha (Incoterms 2020) | risk-transfer: on unloading at named place
packing: Compressors palletised and shrink-wrapped; refrigerant in DOT-approved cylinders | hs-code: 8414.30
inspection: Goods-inward QC within 3 business days of receipt | basis: visual + serial-number match to packing list

text: Partial shipment is permitted for line 4 (telematics) provided the full quantity is delivered no later than the delivery deadline above.

section: 6. Commercial Terms

payment: Net 45 from goods-inward acceptance | method: bank transfer | currency: QAR
warranty: All parts free from defects in material and workmanship | owner: Vendor | period: 18 months from delivery
sla: Critical spare replacement | target: 72h | priority: P1 | scope: lines 1-3
retention: 5% of line 4 amount held until telematics commissioning sign-off | release: on acceptance certificate

clause: Title to goods | passes: on full payment | note: risk passes per delivery term above
clause: Price firmness | basis: prices fixed for this PO; no escalation | exception: documented R-452A index move > 8%

obligation: Provide calibration certificates for all temperature probes | owner: Vendor | by: 2026-07-22
obligation: Register telematics gateways to Marsa fleet account | owner: Vendor | by: 2026-07-29

